definition.value: A branched amino nonasaccharide derivative that is beta-D-Man-(1->4)-beta-D-GlcNAc-(1->4)-D-GlcNAc in which the mannosyl group is substituted at positions 3 and 6 by beta-D-Gal-(1->4)-beta-D-GlcNAc-(1->2)-alpha-D-Man groups.
A D-xylofuranose that has alpha configuration at the anomeric centre.

A branched amino octasaccharide derivative that is beta-D-Man-(1->4)-beta-D-GlcNAc-(1->4)-beta-D-GlcNAc in which the mannosyl group is substituted at position 3 by a beta-D-Gal-(1->4)-beta-D-GlcNAc-(1->2)-alpha-D-Man group and at position 6 by a beta-D-GlcNAc-(1->2)-alpha-D-Man group.
